 management where since  he was senior investment strategist and head portfolio analysis from  he held senior portfolio roles with siemens in the financial services division he started his career in private banking with hauckbankiers in frankfurt helmut kotschwar is a cfa charter holder and holds a master’s degree in economics from the hwv of kassel germany thomas zbinden – senior portfolio manager a swiss citizen  mr zbinden has joined from swisscanto where since  he was senior portfolio manager from  he held senior equity portfolio roles with credit suisse asset management and private banking he started his career with bank von ernst  cie in berne thomas zbinden is an effas certified analyst and holds a degree in economics from the university of berne christoph lang – portfolio manager a german citizen  mr lang has joined from zurich kantonal bank where since  he was senior quant portfolio manager he conducted his traineeship with zkb and with standard chartered bank christoph lang is a cfa charter holder and holds a degree in economics and business administration from the university of hohenheim germany     media release with pictures       back links reports  publicationscompany informationj safra sarasin news registrationarchive of media releases media relations contact t     email you have to activate javascript for displaying this email address to the top × login eservices  online services the accesses to eservices  online services are available on the appropriate country websites please select your country or territory bahamas gibraltar luxembourg monaco switzerland × disclaimer you are about to leave the website of j safra sarasin group please be aware that the external sites of third parties linked to our website are not under our control and as such not verified by us we are therefore in no way liable for their legal compliance andor content and expressly draw your attention to the fact that the views and opinions expressed and any advice subsequently off